text: Jay Warn is an English actor. He was born in Leytonstone, London, and went on to attend the Italia Conti Academy of Theatre Arts in Clapham from 2011–2014, majoring in acting. He has worked at the Open Door Theatre, the Bridewell Theatre, and the Albany Theatre.
